storyInfo: Sesa gets another lead from Passenger about the accident.

attributes.content: Even broken materials like these continue to thirst and scream.
attributes.name: Sesa

attributes.content: Ah, I can hear your wails...
attributes.name: Sesa

attributes.content: Morning, Sesa. Been busy all night again?
attributes.name: Aging Resident

attributes.content: I thought I heard a bunch of mercenaries fighting. Turned out it's just you taking out the trash.
attributes.name: Aging Resident

attributes.content: Time does not forgive!
attributes.name: Sesa

attributes.content: Great power must be tempered by years...
attributes.name: Sesa

attributes.content: In order to break free from the shackles of pain and destruction, right?
attributes.name: Aging Resident

attributes.content: Haha, always so hard to understand what you're saying.
attributes.name: Aging Resident

attributes.content: I'll leave you to it, then.
attributes.name: Aging Resident

attributes.content: One moment.
attributes.name: Sesa

attributes.content: Hm?
attributes.name: Aging Resident

attributes.content: I am not your antidote, and you need not thank me for this act of impulse.
attributes.name: Sesa

attributes.content: However...
attributes.name: Sesa

attributes.content: Is this... did you make this out of that scrap?!
attributes.name: Aging Resident

attributes.content: Just like that? Incredible!
attributes.name: Aging Resident

attributes.content: This old leg of mine hasn't moved so well in... forever! Wow!
attributes.name: Aging Resident

attributes.content: Just gave it a few tweaks.
attributes.name: Sesa

attributes.content: May it solve some of your troubles.
attributes.name: Sesa

attributes.content: You're too humble.
attributes.name: Aging Resident

attributes.content: Thank you so much, Sesa.
attributes.name: Aging Resident

attributes.content: Look out behind you!
attributes.name: Aging Resident

attributes.content: Ouch!
attributes.name: Child

attributes.content: Be careful.
attributes.name: Sesa

attributes.content: It is perilous to keep one's gaze lowered and lose sight of all around you.
attributes.name: Sesa

attributes.content: No idea what you just said!
attributes.name: Child

attributes.content: But it doesn't matter!
attributes.name: Child

attributes.content: Here, Sesa!
attributes.name: Child

attributes.content: Bread?
attributes.name: Sesa

attributes.content: Yeah! I got it from a guy who wears weird clothes and talks weird.
attributes.name: Child

attributes.content: Heh, I got two, actually.
attributes.name: Child

attributes.content: So one's for you. Thanks for catching that thief!
attributes.name: Child

attributes.content: Thank you.
attributes.name: Sesa

attributes.content: Mm-hm!
attributes.name: Child

attributes.content: (Swallows)
attributes.name: Child

attributes.content: What is it?!
attributes.name: Sesa

attributes.content: (There's a note in the bread?)
attributes.name: Sesa

attributes.content: (Someone who dresses and speaks oddly... could it be?)
attributes.name: Sesa

attributes.content: Little one?
attributes.name: Sesa

attributes.content: (Swallows) Mm?
attributes.name: Child

attributes.content: Come, reveal your secrets. Who has guided you here...
attributes.name: Sesa

attributes.content: Sesa?
attributes.name: Aging Resident

attributes.content: Are you Mr. Sesa?
No need for titles. I am beneath them.
attributes.name: Sesa

attributes.content: The aura of a profiteer, that chilling accent...
attributes.name: Sesa

attributes.content: I beg your pardon?
Er, has there been a misunderstanding?
The name's Darrell. I'm a merchant from Columbia.
(A merchant from Columbia?)
attributes.name: Sesa

attributes.content: (Could the note have been a warning?)
attributes.name: Sesa

attributes.content: I've been told you're an expert on retrofitting Originium weapons.
attributes.name: Darrell

attributes.content: So...
attributes.name: Darrell

attributes.content: (Whisper) I have a shipment of... said weapons... from a certain Columbian company.
attributes.name: Darrell

attributes.content: (Whisper) Would you like to have a... chat?
attributes.name: Darrell

attributes.content: I thought this would be a place where I could catch my breath, compared to all the crap in Ursus.
attributes.name: Timid Resident

attributes.content: Yes, I was a killer! But I only ever killed that blasted drunkard in the search squad, dammit!
attributes.name: Timid Resident

attributes.content: I just want to live a quiet life and take care of my new wife.
attributes.name: Timid Resident

attributes.content: I've even tried to stop thinking about the scum who reported me, about what they did to me!
attributes.name: Timid Resident

attributes.content: But why...
attributes.name: Timid Resident

attributes.content: What would you like me to do for you, then?
attributes.name: Passenger

attributes.content: A few Ursus mercenaries recognized me. I denied it, but they burned down my shop...
attributes.name: Timid Resident

attributes.content: The Lord Ameer's men chased them away, but... I know they've set their sights on me.
attributes.name: Timid Resident

attributes.content: So...
attributes.name: Timid Resident

attributes.content: Why did you come to me, then?
attributes.name: Passenger

attributes.content: What drove you to forfeit your own rights?
attributes.name: Passenger

attributes.content: Rights?
attributes.name: Timid Resident

attributes.content: I know you can find them.
attributes.name: Timid Resident

attributes.content: But you could have done it yourself.
attributes.name: Passenger

attributes.content: Am I wrong? Are you suddenly beset by pity for your fellow man?
attributes.name: Passenger

attributes.content: To my knowledge, it wasn't just some 'search squad member' you killed in Ursus.
attributes.name: Passenger

attributes.content: You!
attributes.name: Timid Resident

attributes.content: I'll consider this a sign of your mistrust in me. A test, as it were.
attributes.name: Passenger

attributes.content: But see, you clearly know what you want, don't you?
attributes.name: Passenger

attributes.content: I'm sorry...
attributes.name: Timid Resident

attributes.content: That said, that weapon of yours isn't exactly suitable for revenge.
attributes.name: Passenger

attributes.content: What do you want?
attributes.name: Timid Resident

attributes.content: What can you give me?
attributes.name: Passenger

attributes.content: I'll accept all reasonable forms of payment, even... interesting conditions.
attributes.name: Passenger

attributes.content: Goodbye.
attributes.name: Timid Resident

attributes.content: I could help you.
attributes.name: Passenger

attributes.content: Don't worry, I'm just looking for a purpose.
attributes.name: Passenger

attributes.content: A purpose?
attributes.name: Timid Resident

attributes.content: Yes, a purpose.
attributes.name: Passenger

attributes.content: Thanks, but no.
attributes.name: Timid Resident

attributes.content: This is rather unlike you. I thought you'd have come earlier.
attributes.name: Passenger

attributes.content: Or even barged in, rather than standing there like a student waiting for his teacher's answer.
attributes.name: Passenger

attributes.content: Of course, I could consider taking in a student like you.
attributes.name: Passenger

attributes.content: Give you some necessary pointers, if that's what you're looking for.
attributes.name: Passenger

attributes.content: I do need an answer.
attributes.name: Sesa

attributes.content: That note. You're the only one who could've sent it.
attributes.name: Sesa

attributes.content: I don't know the child.
attributes.name: Passenger

attributes.content: So?
attributes.name: Sesa

attributes.content: But I do 'know' them.
attributes.name: Passenger

attributes.content: I was handing out bread to every child on the streets who passed by, knowing the message would make it to you.
attributes.name: Passenger

attributes.content: I was asking why, not how.
attributes.name: Sesa

attributes.content: Did you think you were clever, following and using a child?
attributes.name: Sesa

attributes.content: I was simply... matching my behavior to yours.
attributes.name: Passenger

attributes.content: What?
attributes.name: Sesa

attributes.content: The caution and wariness you've shown in Sargon... You must be hiding from someone.
attributes.name: Passenger

attributes.content: The less traces one leaves, the harder it will be for someone to find out.
attributes.name: Passenger

attributes.content: Can you talk normally for once?
attributes.name: Sesa

attributes.content: Who, me?
attributes.name: Passenger

attributes.content: A merchant who says he's from Columbia, claiming to have experimental weapons from that company.
attributes.name: Sesa

attributes.content: Did you think I'd believe it's a coincidence? What do you want?
attributes.name: Sesa

attributes.content: It's been many years. Have you found a single thing?
attributes.name: Passenger

attributes.content: This isn't the first time you've done something like this.
attributes.name: Sesa

attributes.content: Are you having fun?
attributes.name: Sesa

attributes.content: You give me a piece of intel, then watch me blunder around and end up empty-handed.
attributes.name: Sesa

attributes.content: But you'll keep searching. Because vengeance is the eternal motif.
attributes.name: Passenger

attributes.content: How far will you go?
attributes.name: Passenger

attributes.content: Also, you shouldn't get the wrong idea.
attributes.name: Passenger

attributes.content: I wanted to help you, and to help myself as well.
attributes.name: Passenger

attributes.content: What do you want?
attributes.name: Sesa

attributes.content: Did you accept his offer?
attributes.name: Passenger

attributes.content: No, I told him I wasn't interested.
attributes.name: Sesa

attributes.content: I turned him down and told him to never come back.
attributes.name: Sesa

attributes.content: Oh?
attributes.name: Passenger

attributes.content: What a surprising result. I was sure you'd gladly accept it...
attributes.name: Passenger

attributes.content: Did you not trust his identity? Or did you suspect my motives?
attributes.name: Passenger

attributes.content: What do you want?
attributes.name: Sesa

attributes.content: What can you give me?
attributes.name: Passenger

attributes.content: I'll accept all reasonable forms of payment, even... interesting conditions.
attributes.name: Passenger

attributes.content: Alright. But no more conditions. You've already named your price.
attributes.name: Sesa

attributes.content: You said you wanted a purpose.
attributes.name: Sesa

attributes.content: I'll give you one.
attributes.name: Sesa

attributes.content: Deal.
attributes.name: Passenger

attributes.content: So, what do you know?
attributes.name: Sesa

attributes.content: He's not a merchant. Everything he said was a clumsy lie.
attributes.name: Passenger

attributes.content: Even I could see that. That's why I found him suspicious.
attributes.name: Sesa

attributes.content: But you knew that and still sent him to me. You must have your reasons.
attributes.name: Sesa

attributes.content: He showed me a weapon sample from Columbia.
attributes.name: Passenger

attributes.content: It was... interesting.
attributes.name: Passenger

attributes.content: The Originium Arts mechanism was more direct than any other product in the black market.
attributes.name: Passenger

attributes.content: Do you mean...
attributes.name: Sesa

attributes.content: Compared to your research, the technology used was crude, immature.
attributes.name: Passenger

attributes.content: But someone is trying to pick a lock which should not be opened.
attributes.name: Passenger

attributes.content: No one should see a single page of that documentation ever again, much less sell it on the black market.
attributes.name: Sesa

attributes.content: It's a valuable lead.
attributes.name: Passenger

attributes.content: Or perhaps bait. A trap.
attributes.name: Passenger

attributes.content: Yes, the perfect bait for me. One that I couldn't resist.
attributes.name: Sesa

attributes.content: Brother...
attributes.name: Sesa

attributes.content: May I ask what your plans are now?
attributes.name: Passenger

attributes.content: I cannot say.
attributes.name: Sesa

attributes.content: What about making a new deal?
attributes.name: Passenger

attributes.content: You'll need my help in the black markets of Sargon.
attributes.name: Passenger

attributes.content: No, I would rather place my faith in inspired intuition, rather than the guided hand.
attributes.name: Sesa

attributes.content: The hidden truth will be revealed.
attributes.name: Sesa

attributes.content: Ah... what a shame.
attributes.name: Passenger

attributes.content: How long are you gonna take? I've never seen someone so picky in my life!
attributes.name: Arrogant Merchant

attributes.content: Ealayk allaena!
attributes.name: Arrogant Merchant

attributes.content: What's that attitude? Ibn al kalb!
attributes.name: Young Mercenary

attributes.content: Do you really think any of this crap you're selling is anything but scrap metal?
attributes.name: Young Mercenary

attributes.content: Say that again?! I'll tear you to pieces, I swear!
attributes.name: Arrogant Merchant

attributes.content: Try me! Haram alayk, I wouldn't have wasted my time here if a friend didn't recommend it.
attributes.name: Young Mercenary

attributes.content: Al'ahmaq!
attributes.name: Arrogant Merchant

attributes.content: Who're you?
attributes.name: Young Mercenary

attributes.content: You again!
attributes.name: Arrogant Merchant

attributes.content: All that is sold here is emptiness.
attributes.name: Sesa

attributes.content: Small wonder no gazes linger.
attributes.name: Sesa

attributes.content: Just my luck, what a day!
attributes.name: Arrogant Merchant

attributes.content: First a fool, now a madman.
attributes.name: Arrogant Merchant

attributes.content: Get lost!
attributes.name: Arrogant Merchant

attributes.content: Haha, do you not see the weakness and frailty in his weapons?
attributes.name: Sesa

attributes.content: The imposition of will can hardly disguise foolishness and ineptitude.
attributes.name: Sesa

attributes.content: GET! LOST!
attributes.name: Arrogant Merchant

attributes.content: I wish to bridge the gap to the other side. I know what you seek...
attributes.name: Sesa

attributes.content: I will reveal hidden secrets.
attributes.name: Sesa

attributes.content: Seriously, are you sick or something?
attributes.name: Young Mercenary

attributes.content: What the hell are you talking about?
attributes.name: Young Mercenary

attributes.content: Must have forgotten to take his meds.
attributes.name: Arrogant Merchant

attributes.content: Ah, to be blind and foolish.
attributes.name: Sesa

attributes.content: The weapons from Columbia bring unfathomable destruction and power.
attributes.name: Sesa

attributes.content: They await their destined bearer.
attributes.name: Sesa

attributes.content: What?
attributes.name: Young Mercenary

attributes.content: Farewell.
attributes.name: Sesa

attributes.content: Get lost, and never come back!
attributes.name: Arrogant Merchant

attributes.content: Ealayk allaena!
attributes.name: Arrogant Merchant

attributes.content: What's your problem? Outta my way!
attributes.name: Young Mercenary

attributes.content: What did he say? Weapons from Columbia?
attributes.name: Arrogant Merchant

attributes.content: How would I know?! Piss off!
attributes.name: Young Mercenary

attributes.content: Columbian weapons...
attributes.name: Arrogant Merchant

attributes.content: (Drunkenly) One more mug!
attributes.name: Darrell

attributes.content: (Drunkenly) *Hic* The people here...
attributes.name: Darrell

attributes.content: (Drunkenly) Dumb *hic* peasants...
attributes.name: Darrell

attributes.content: (Drunkenly) They *hic* have no idea *hic* about the stuff I have!
attributes.name: Darrell

attributes.content: I think you've had too much.
attributes.name: Barkeeper

attributes.content: (Drunkenly) Idiots! *Hic*
attributes.name: Darrell

attributes.content: (Drunkenly) I thought I could *hic* make a killing off it...
attributes.name: Darrell

attributes.content: (Drunkenly) The stuff's so good *hic*... why won't anyone take it?
attributes.name: Darrell

attributes.content: Hey there, friend.
attributes.name: Arrogant Merchant

attributes.content: (Drunkenly) *Hic*...
attributes.name: Darrell

attributes.content: Hey!
Who's there?!
attributes.name: Arrogant Merchant

attributes.content: I saw you shadowing him.
What are you up to?
Allaenat ealayk!
attributes.name: Arrogant Merchant

attributes.content: None of your business!
attributes.name: Arrogant Merchant

attributes.content: What are you up to?!
Out of my way!
attributes.name: Arrogant Merchant

attributes.content: Ugh...
Help! Thief!
Allaenat ealayk!
attributes.name: Arrogant Merchant

attributes.content: Hey!
attributes.name: Arrogant Merchant

attributes.content: (Drunkenly) Huh? *Hic* What d'ya want?
attributes.name: Darrell

attributes.content: You're coming with me.
attributes.name: Arrogant Merchant

attributes.content: (Drunkenly) Ow!
attributes.name: Darrell

attributes.content: This is... my room...
attributes.name: Darrell

attributes.content: How did I...
attributes.name: Darrell

attributes.content: Whoa!
attributes.name: Darrell

attributes.content: W-Who are you?
attributes.name: Darrell

attributes.content: You're awake? Where are the goods?
attributes.name: Arrogant Merchant

attributes.content: W-What goods?
attributes.name: Darrell

attributes.content: Don't play dumb with me. You've been telling anyone who would listen that you have a bunch of Columbian weapons.
attributes.name: Arrogant Merchant

attributes.content: You wanted to do business. Well, I'm here to do business.
attributes.name: Arrogant Merchant

attributes.content: Business...
attributes.name: Darrell

attributes.content: Who the hell does business like this?!
attributes.name: Darrell

attributes.content: I want to see a sample. Now.
attributes.name: Arrogant Merchant

attributes.content: Business is all about trust. I'm sure you understand.
attributes.name: Arrogant Merchant

attributes.content: Behind that cupboard.
attributes.name: Darrell

attributes.content: Ow! Why you—!
attributes.name: Darrell

attributes.content: Aren't you gonna show me a sample? Is this how you treat your customers?
attributes.name: Arrogant Merchant

attributes.content: No wonder you couldn't sell anything.
attributes.name: Arrogant Merchant

attributes.content: (Even project leads like my brother couldn't have taken experimental weapons out of the labs, much less sold them abroad.)
attributes.name: Sesa

attributes.content: (So who is this man? Is he really just elaborate bait?)
attributes.name: Sesa

attributes.content: (The terrible acting, the obvious lies...)
attributes.name: Sesa

attributes.content: Here... your sample.
attributes.name: Darrell

attributes.content: Well, well! Very fine indeed.
attributes.name: Arrogant Merchant

attributes.content: O-Of course! It's cutting-edge technology!
attributes.name: Darrell

attributes.content: Simple to maintain, and, er... easy to use.
attributes.name: Darrell

attributes.content: Even for laymen...
attributes.name: Darrell

attributes.content: Show me how.
attributes.name: Arrogant Merchant

attributes.content: W-What?
attributes.name: Darrell

attributes.content: But I'm not a mercenary...
attributes.name: Darrell

attributes.content: So what? Didn't you say it's easy to use?
attributes.name: Arrogant Merchant

attributes.content: It's your product. You demonstrate it.
attributes.name: Arrogant Merchant

attributes.content: Allaenat ealayk!
attributes.name: Arrogant Merchant

attributes.content: Don't point that thing at me! I'll kill you!
attributes.name: Arrogant Merchant

attributes.content: I-I think it's this one here...?
attributes.name: Darrell

attributes.content: You don't even know how use your own goods?
attributes.name: Arrogant Merchant

attributes.content: I-I do! I do!
attributes.name: Darrell

attributes.content: Activate the Originium... then press the trigger.
attributes.name: Darrell

attributes.content: I told you not to point that thing at me!
attributes.name: Arrogant Merchant

attributes.content: Allaenat ealayk!
attributes.name: Arrogant Merchant

attributes.content: Enough!
attributes.name: Darrell

attributes.content: Enough!!
attributes.name: Darrell

attributes.content: Don't touch me again! I'm warning you!
attributes.name: Darrell

attributes.content: Al'ama! What are you doing?!
attributes.name: Arrogant Merchant

attributes.content: Down payment! You wanna do business, you make a down payment!
attributes.name: Darrell

attributes.content: You want money? You haven't shown me any goods!
attributes.name: Arrogant Merchant

attributes.content: This weapon is really powerful!
attributes.name: Darrell

attributes.content: All you need to do is press the trigger! Wanna see for yourself?
attributes.name: Darrell

attributes.content: How many do you have? The same model as the one you're holding?
attributes.name: Arrogant Merchant

attributes.content: T-Tons of 'em!
attributes.name: Darrell

attributes.content: I'll have someone tell you where the deal takes place once I get my down payment!
attributes.name: Darrell

attributes.content: How do I know you're not playing me for a fool?
attributes.name: Arrogant Merchant

attributes.content: You saw it with your own eyes!
attributes.name: Darrell

attributes.content: The form, the technology, none of this is possible in Sargon.
attributes.name: Darrell

attributes.content: Very well...
attributes.name: Arrogant Merchant

attributes.content: Alright, friend, I suppose did get a little carried away.
attributes.name: Arrogant Merchant

attributes.content: How much are you asking?
attributes.name: Arrogant Merchant

attributes.content: Ibn al kalb! You're trying to threaten me?!
attributes.name: Arrogant Merchant

attributes.content: I'll kill you!
attributes.name: Arrogant Merchant

attributes.content: Whoa!
attributes.name: Darrell

attributes.content: *cough* *cough*...
attributes.name: Darrell

attributes.content: Ow ow ow!
attributes.name: Darrell

attributes.content: Don't move, unless you want to die.
W-What?
attributes.name: Darrell

attributes.content: That weapon won't help you. I know it better than you do.
Who are you? Where did this sample come from?
One... two...
I'll talk, I'll talk!
attributes.name: Darrell

attributes.content: I really am from Columbia...
attributes.name: Darrell

attributes.content: Allaenat ealayk!
attributes.name: Arrogant Merchant

attributes.content: Who hit me?!
attributes.name: Arrogant Merchant

attributes.content: Whoa!
attributes.name: Arrogant Merchant

attributes.content: If you hadn't acted, the prototype would have overloaded and exploded, wiping away all traces.
attributes.name: Passenger

attributes.content: But instead, you saved his life, without even ascertaining his identity.
attributes.name: Passenger

attributes.content: A bout of adventurism? Or simple sentimentality?
attributes.name: Passenger

attributes.content: I'm not out to kill people. I just want to know the truth.
attributes.name: Sesa

attributes.content: Did you find the answer you wanted?
attributes.name: Passenger

attributes.content: You're an employee at that company?
I've had a lot of business dealings with them. But I've never seen you.
I-I'm just a low-level worker in Logistics and Maintenance. You probably never met me.
attributes.name: Darrell

attributes.content: Logistics and Maintenance... how did you get the weapon?
We're in charge of transporting and scrapping discarded prototypes.
attributes.name: Darrell

attributes.content: I found this off the scrap heap.
attributes.name: Darrell

attributes.content: Scrapped prototypes? How many more like this do you have?
None! This is the only one!
attributes.name: Darrell

attributes.content: That's not what you said earlier.
I-I was lying to him!
attributes.name: Darrell

attributes.content: Oh?
But I'm telling the truth now!
attributes.name: Darrell

attributes.content: There were only so many of them, and most were completely destroyed.
attributes.name: Darrell

attributes.content: My thinking was that the people here would never chase me down to Columbia, even if they never got the goods.
attributes.name: Darrell

attributes.content: A few years back, your company claimed that an accident had occurred at the lab, preventing them from delivering a shipment.
Did that really happen?
A few years back...
attributes.name: Darrell

attributes.content: Yeah, there was a serious accident at a lab.
attributes.name: Darrell

attributes.content: But I don't know what happened... we arrived on the scene afterward.
attributes.name: Darrell

attributes.content: Did you notice anything unusual?
Hmm... Not really.
attributes.name: Darrell

attributes.content: But the company removed every piece of scrap from the scene in individual containers.
attributes.name: Darrell

attributes.content: Individual containers? Where were they taken?
I don't know.
attributes.name: Darrell

attributes.content: I really don't know! Honest!
attributes.name: Darrell

attributes.content: Everyone was searched before we left, to make sure none of us took anything.
attributes.name: Darrell

attributes.content: I swear I'm telling the truth!
attributes.name: Darrell

attributes.content: Please, don't kill me!
attributes.name: Darrell

attributes.content: Did you spare his life out of a sense of conscience, or as a valuable lead?
attributes.name: Passenger

attributes.content: No need to feel embarrassed. None of us act without a reason.
attributes.name: Passenger

attributes.content: Not that the results are always what we wanted.
attributes.name: Passenger

attributes.content: And is this what you wanted?
attributes.name: Sesa

attributes.content: To see me feeling lost, helpless, angry?
attributes.name: Sesa

attributes.content: I just wanted to know the answer.
attributes.name: Passenger

attributes.content: To what?
attributes.name: Sesa

attributes.content: How far you would go for revenge.
attributes.name: Passenger

attributes.content: However far it takes.
attributes.name: Sesa

attributes.content: Is that so?
attributes.name: Passenger

attributes.content: What about the researchers?
What?
attributes.name: Darrell

attributes.content: Did any researchers from the lab survive the accident?
I-I don't think so...
attributes.name: Darrell

attributes.content: (Deep breath)
Your department disposed of the bodies, didn't it? Where were they taken?
I heard from their families that they never saw the bodies. They were just told that they had died in the accident.
The bodies...
attributes.name: Darrell

attributes.content: (Deep breath)
Yes, the bodies!
They were all sent to garbage disposal.
attributes.name: Darrell

attributes.content: What?!
'It always ends the same way.'
attributes.name: Passenger

attributes.content: 'I tried my best. I always fail, but I'll do anything. Anything for some closure.' Isn't that right?
attributes.name: Passenger

attributes.content: Are you done?
attributes.name: Sesa

attributes.content: No plots, no traps, no ulterior motives.
attributes.name: Passenger

attributes.content: Maybe they have no interest in your investigation. Maybe they've completely forgotten about you.
attributes.name: Passenger

attributes.content: Worthless.
attributes.name: Passenger

attributes.content: What do you want from me?
attributes.name: Sesa

attributes.content: How far you will go for revenge?
attributes.name: Passenger

attributes.content: I'm sorry! They were sent to garbage disposal!
attributes.name: Darrell

attributes.content: Whether intact or damaged, they were all just... there was no order from above.
attributes.name: Darrell

attributes.content: We just disposed of them according to standard procedures.
attributes.name: Darrell

attributes.content: Please!
attributes.name: Darrell

attributes.content: Please, don't kill me!
attributes.name: Darrell

attributes.content: You know it wasn't his fault. He's insignificant.
attributes.name: Passenger

attributes.content: But you don't want to let anything go, no matter how slim the chance, how flimsy the link.
attributes.name: Passenger

attributes.content: As long as you achieve your purpose.
attributes.name: Passenger

attributes.content: Vengeance is the eternal motif.
attributes.name: Passenger

attributes.content: Like you? Burning down a whole city without any concern for those within?
attributes.name: Sesa

attributes.content: I gave them time to evacuate.
attributes.name: Passenger

attributes.content: Yes, you made the relatively correct choice in the circumstances, one that saved you face.
attributes.name: Sesa

attributes.content: But I completed my revenge. What about you?
